    <span class="author" data-post-author="stickboy54321"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/civis/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=334262&amp;sid=f449b80a7e86d068201129d0b8455a6e">stickboy54321</a></span><span class="rank">Smack-Fu Master, in training</span>
